  • Classes in io.github.msdk.datamodel.featuretables used by io.github.msdk.datamodel.featuretables 
    Class and Description
    ColumnName
    Represents the name of the feature table columns.
    FeatureTable
    A feature table consists of a list of named columns, each with a specific type for the values contained in it.
    FeatureTableColumn
    A feature table column has a name, a fixed type for its element values, and an optional Sample associated to it.
    FeatureTableDataConverter
    Convert data from a source feature table row and column to a target row and column.
    FeatureTableRow
    FeatureTableRow interface.
    Sample
    Sample interface.
